<section>
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    Health Toolkit is a simple Node.js + Express app using EJS views and MySQL.
    It helps you track achievements, medications, and period logs, and provides
    quick fitness calculators.
  </p>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Authentication: register, login, and session-based access</li>
    <li>Achievements: add, search, export CSV, weekly trend insights</li>
    <li>Medication Tracker: interval, daily, or weekly schedules</li>
    <li>Period Logs: record start dates and estimate next window</li>
    <li>Fitness Tools: BMI, BMR/TDEE, Heart Rate zones, Macros, Water intake</li>
    <li>Nutrition Lookup: powered by CalorieNinjas API</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data & Privacy</h2>
  <p>
    Your data is stored in a local MySQL database. Actions are recorded in an
    audit log to help trace activity. No third-party trackers are used. The
    Nutrition lookup sends food queries to CalorieNinjas.
  </p>

